<p><span class="anchor" id="p63"></span>وَيصدق الْمَالِك فِي عَددهَا ان كَانَ ثِقَة والا<a href="#p63" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p64"></span>بِأَن لم يكن ثِقَة<a href="#p64" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
